task.summary: removed some code from REST_Admin_API so it won't give errors at run
now we are able to see all the classes, the semesters and the periods. we can also add semesters and periods.
Now we are able to see all classes, to see the semesters for a class and the periods for a semester. Moreover, we can add semesters for a specific class and periods for a specific semester.
Now we are able to see tasks for a period, as well as to add tasks for a specific period
Now we can see and add students. We can see a student's points for a task or a period.

When we add a task for a period, all the students from that period are assigned the task. When we add new student for a period, the student is assigned all the tasks from the period. Now we can give points for a student for a task and see the total achieved and required points for a student for a period.
Now we can add and see a photo for each student :) - By Cristi
made a nice view for assigning points
